No worries! This is Tim from Pearl (www.trypearl.io) we're a UCLA based startup helping connect students with tech jobs.
Hello I found an opportunity so I'm no longer looking for opportunities.
No worries. Still looking for Summer internships in Product Management!
You can start by letting me know what sorts of roles you’re looking for!

The reason I ask is because our list of open jobs is relatively small compared to the number of job seekers we have here. So in reality, most people don't get any job invites on Pearl. We want to provide a better experience for people than this status quo, so our team is brainstorming how we can add value in other ways

This is in contrast with how we've been running things. Typically we'll sign a contract with a employer first and then send out their jobs. But the downside to that is we have limited opportunities, so a lot of people don't get any messages from us.
